{"id": "art-1171", "label": "Art. 1171", "title": "Art. 1171", "slug": "art-1171", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1898463821\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2317\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1898463821\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 117<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_71143726\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2316\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_71143726\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Au dreptul de a cere introducerea unor noi puncte pe\nordinea de zi unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span> reprezentând, individual sau împreun&#259;,\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 5% din capitalul social.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1263362394\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2315\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1263362394\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Cererile se înainteaz&#259; consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv directoratului, în cel mult\n15 zile de la publicarea convoc&#259;rii, în vederea public&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> aducerii acestora la <span class=SpellE>cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;</span>\n<span class=SpellE>celorlal&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>.\nÎn cazul în care pe ordinea de zi figureaz&#259; numirea administratorilor,\nrespectiv a membrilor consiliului de supraveghere, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> doresc s&#259; formuleze propuneri de\ncandidaturi, în cerere vor fi incluse <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span>\ncu privire la numele, localitatea de domiciliu <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncalificarea profesional&#259; ale persoanelor propuse pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;iile</span> respective.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_433009367\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2314\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_433009367\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(2<sup>1</sup>)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\npoate s&#259; modifice convocatorul dup&#259; momentul public&#259;rii\nacestuia, în termen de cel mult 15 zile de la momentul public&#259;rii.</span></u><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1238575173\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2313\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1238575173\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)</span><span class=SpellE><s><span style='color:#E51C23'>Ordinea</span></s><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>Convocatorul</span></u></span><u><span style='color:#569748'>\nmodificat cuprinzând, dup&#259; caz, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ordinea</span></u><span\nstyle='color:black'> de zi completat&#259; cu punctele propuse de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span></span><u><span style='color:#569748'> sau de\nc&#259;tre consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span></span></u><span\nstyle='color:black'>, ulterior convoc&#259;rii, trebuie </span><span\nclass=SpellE><s><span style='color:#E51C23'>publicat&#259;</span></s><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>publicat</span></u></span><span style='color:black'> cu\nîndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> prev&#259;zute de <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau\nde actul constitutiv pentru convocarea adun&#259;rii generale, cu cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 10 zile înaintea adun&#259;rii generale, la data\n<span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionat&#259;</span> în convocatorul <span\nclass=SpellE>ini&#355;ial</span>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}